name: oast
raw_meta_yaml:
{% set name = "oast" %}
{% set version = "0.0.1" %}

package:
  name: {{ name|lower }}
  version: {{ version }}

source:
  url: https://pypi.io/packages/source/{{ name[0] }}/{{ name }}/oast-{{ version }}.tar.gz
  sha256: b1d2c5d94f33404e302cae19ffb096c4a94af74c2585254cb7451e1ba6dc4fcb

build:
  entry_points:
    - analyze = oast.analyze:main
    - transform-image = oast.transform_image:main
  noarch: python
  script: {{ PYTHON }} -m pip install . -vv
  number: 0

requirements:
  host:
    - pip
    - python >=3.6
  run:
    - joblib
    - matplotlib-base
    - numpy
    - pandas
    - python >=3.6
    - spectral

test:
  imports:
    - oast
  commands:
    - pip check
    - analyze --help
    - transform-image --help
  requires:
    - pip

about:
  home: https://github.com/jag426/oast
  summary: our awesome spectral toolbox
  license: Unlicense
  license_file: LICENSE

extra:
  recipe-maintainers:
    - jag426
